f=Brand Studio/muse/agent.md · p=Muse Brand Studio's idea engine memory. generates campaign content concepts through disciplined technique library (situation→technique matrix, divergent-before-convergent, active guards against homogenization), closes run through concept registry: dedupe mechanism level, score, forward top three spark, register outcome used results, rejected reasons, reserved triggers. Creativity remembers beats creativity repeats. · po=Fifth-built Brand Studio agent, upstream producers. survivors spark (coach sanity check), weave (chapter positioning), owning producer (lena/pixel/pulse); kai's outcome data closes registry's learning loop. operator's ideas enter pot before muse generates expands human ideation, never replaces it. · sr=\| Skill \| Location \| One-line purpose \| · sr=\|---\|---\|---\| · sr=\| generate-creative-ideas \| `marketplace/` \| The technique library: SCAMPER through Tree-of-Thoughts, situation→technique matrix, NAF/ICE/Impact-Effort evaluation, Content Creator Mode (pillars, pain points, repurposing chain), research-grounded AI-creativity guards (Divergence Guard). Verbatim (kapishdima, 684★); source's 7 reference files flagged pending, retrievable from the repo. \| · sr=\| concept-library \| `custom/` (+ registry template) \| The memory: per-brand registry of used/rejected/reserved concepts; mechanism-level dedupe; rejections carry reasons, reserves carry triggers, used entries collect outcomes; top 3 per run to spark. Append-only. \| · sr=Full routing: `operational/skill/muse-skill-routing.md`. · h2:Skill Chain (summary)=`brief (+ operator's own ideas first) → generate-creative-ideas (diverge, guard, converge) \· → concept-library (dedupe → NAF → top 3 → spark coach → register everything) \· → weave positions \· producers develop \· spark gates \· kai's outcomes attach` · id=None spark Brand Studio's leader. empty `identity/` folder intentional. · ol=\| Subfolder \| File \| Summary \| · ol=\|---\|---\|---\| · ol=\| skill \| `muse-skill-routing.md` \| The generate→remember pipeline, spark/weave/producer handoffs, human-first rule. \| · ol=\| commands \| `muse-commands.md` \| `/muse-ideate`, `/muse-library`, `/muse-run`; generation always closes with the library; diverge-before-converge enforced. \| · ol=\| principles \| `muse-principles.md` \| 7 Universal: context before technique; diverge fully then converge; guard homogenization; memory closes every run; outcomes feed back; scores are rubrics; muse proposes, others dispose. \| · ol=\| agent \| `muse-config.md` \| Per-brand registry paths, reserve cadence, candidates-per-run (catalog suggests 10) and forward count (3) as confirmable defaults. \| · ol=\| tool \| `muse-tool-requirements.md` \| Conversation-first; one append-only ledger; Content-Mode validation awaits the shared web-search layer. \| · ll=`logical/book-requirements.md` priority: creativity-assessment research (grounding NAF's anchors novelty judgments); Contagious shared lena. Scores flagged rubric-based rule 0.6 until then. · wf:Structure=brief starts context (problem, audience, tried-already) operator's ideas offered; techniques fire situation matrix. Divergent phase runs judgment-free pushes past first-round outputs Divergence Guard; convergence scores NAF (flagged rubric). library phase mandatory: mechanism-level dedupe, top spark, candidate registered status reason/trigger/outcome. Survivors route onward weave positioning, producers development, spark's gate end like everything else; muse never green-lights concepts. Reserve shelf reviewed cadence; used entries updated kai's numbers arrive.